      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Progressive pacer APOLLOSTORM (2) has led to win his two starts here off a lengthy spell, cruising home by a big space fresh then working forward from wider last week and proving too strong. Has the speed to take advantage of a low draw so can land the hat trick. KARTIARE (9) continues to a run of second row draws but has been racing well from there including a fresh win three back and a narrow defeat from this barrier last time. Should be at his peak now. Go well again. HOORAH PHILTRA (8) draws for a trail and his form is hard to knock having recorded two wins and a nose second from his last three outings at this circuit and distance. ODIN (7) draws wide again but continued his consistent form when fourth from this barrier last time so include.",
